title: I’m Still Freaked Out by the Real Estate Market (Hour 1)
description:
Dave Ramsey & Kristina Ellis discuss:

Being freaked out by the housing market,

How to figure out what baby step you're on,

Paying off student loans with retirement funds,

Student loan forgiveness updates.
